    title: 'Training and Development',
    description:
      'A well trained person goes up high in his own esteem, and derives better job satisfaction from his work. Often, skills become obsolete so,  employees need to update their skills to cope with the new challenges.<br/><br/>At Ray Business Technologies, the attraction, development and retention of talent is the top priority. Our training programs are prevailing way to meet the complex learning and performance requirements. We provide a flexible learning approach, which will help people to be more versatile. This will in-turn help the entire organization to be more agile in the marketplace.<br/><br/>We at Raybiztech continuously strive to contribute towards associates development and growth. To empower our associates with requisite skills and abilities, We provide various training programmes such as:<br/><b><br/>Personality Development<br/></b>The personality development program at raybiztech is an interactive program, offering our associates both professional and personal development. Besides providing opportunities to learn through training, the personality development program enhances and groom one\'s inner and outer self and brings about a positive change. This process encompasses boosting confidence, communication and language speaking capabilities and adding grace and style to the way one looks, walks and talks.<b><br/><br/></b><b>Technical Training <br/></b>Raybiztech provides technical training to all its associates based on the project and training requirements identified in the review. The technical training program delivers training, assessment and consultation to boost and refresh associate skills and knowledge on the latest software development tools, operating systems and enterprise ready applications.<div><br/></div><div>After the Kentico training, it is mandatory for all Kentico professionals to write the Kentico exam. The details are mentioned below;</div><div><br/></div><div><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1.<span>      </span>All Trainees (less than 1 year) should pass Kentico exam within 1 year of joining in max 3 attempts</p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2.<span>      </span>All existing Kentico professionals and new joinees (experience) should pass the Kentico exam in next 1 year in max 3 attempts.</p><br/><b>Communication Skills Training</b><br/>As an organization, we believe that professional excellence requires effective communication, whether it is oral, face to face or written. For this, Raybiztech provides communication skills training to all the associates to communicate fluently with both internal and external customers. The communication skills training will not only refine the workforce, but will lead to operational excellence in the workplace.<br/><b><br/>Process to be followed for conducting training session:</b><br/>1. Raise a request in HIVE<br/>2. Once the ticket is accepted, share the training details(training topic, attendees name, duration of training)<br/>3. HR will raise a ticket in HIVE against the trainer<br/>4. Trainer is requested to conduct the session and mark the attendance in the register<br/>5. If there are any assignments trainer is requested to coordinate with the trainees, evaluate the assignments and share the rating list with HR<br/>6. Once the training is completed trainer is requested to close the training ticket in HIVE and mention the spent hours<br/>7. HR will co ordinate with trainees to collect the feedback<br/><br/><br/></div>',
