    description:
      '<p>Separations: Resignations and Terminations <br/></p>&#10;<p> <b>Resignation</b></p><p>If at any point of your career with us you feel you have to leave, we  request that             you speak to the HR or your immediate supervisor  at the earliest about your plans             so as to help the company  plan a replacement. The Employee can terminate the employment              by giving the company a three month notice in writing. Notwithstanding  this the employee             will be required to serve the company as  long as the company deems required based             on project  deliverable.</p><p>An employee can submit his/her resignation through Separation module in OVH, no direct email would be entertained. For further queries, employees can contact HR department.</p><p><b>Company Initiated Terminations </b><br/></p><p>The company reserves the right to terminate the employee by giving three  months notice             or salary in lieu thereof or release him  immediately without compensation if the performance is found unsatisfactory. However, in the event of the             employee  committing any criminal offense or indulging in activities which amount              to moral turpitude or acting against the interest of the  Company, the concerned             employee shall be liable to be  dismissed forthright after getting an opportunity             of being  heard, without any further notice. Further the Company may terminate  this             contract, without prior notice or payment in lieu of  notice for serious misconduct             in accordance with relevant  laws or any material breach of any of the standards             of  Conduct specified and compensation will not be provided.<br/></p>&#10;<p>On termination of your employment for any reason, the Company will be  entitled to             deduct any amounts the employee owes to the  Company or any of the Group Companies             from amounts owed to  the employee.</p><p>&#10;Company Initiated separations/ Terminations is for reasons deemed fit by  the management             is effected with written notice of intention  to terminate or payment of an equivalent             amount calculated  on basic pay for the un-served period of notice.</p>&#10;<p><strong>Notice requirement shall be as follows:</strong><br/>&#10;<br/>&#10;<b><i>During Probationary Period</i></b><i>: 90 days</i><br/>&#10;<b><i>After Confirmation of Employment</i></b><i>: 90 days </i></p>&#10;<p> <b>Formalities</b></p>&#10;&#10;<ul>&#10;    <li>Knowledge Transfer, Handover and documentation as agreed directed by the reporting                 manager upon intimation</li>&#10;    <li>Return of all official property issued (access and id cards,  manuals, documents,                 etc) and acquired during the course  of employment with the organization.</li>&#10;    <li>The HR would like your detailed feedback</li>&#10;    <li>Please communicate your new address to enable us to communicate with you on your                 benefits, TDS certificate etc.</li></ul><p><b>Early release on Medical ground </b></p><p>Raybiztech understands you may need to take break on your medical grounds. However, there has been number of incidents of fake medical reports and falsehood of health issues. In order to ensure we work in complete compliance and our clients\' interests, you are requested to do the following:</p><p></p><ol><li>Please be informed that hiding truth on fake medical reports is a criminal offence and employer can take appropriate action against you.<br/></li><li>You are hereby advised to not abuse sick leaves or produce fake medical reports<br/></li><li>Please share hard copies your medical reports<br/></li><li>The medical certificate must be issued and signed by a medical practitioner or any other person who is certified to diagnose and treat patients and who is registered with a professional council established.<br/></li><li>Provide medical practitioner\'s address and registration number. Please be informed that the employer can contact the given medical practitioner.<br/></li><li>In case you use medical grounds to leave the company, your relieving letter will be issued only after 90 days. <br/></li><li>In case you use medical grounds to leave the company, you are requested to sign an agreement with the employer for no-job for 90 days. This agreement will state that you will not join any company for next 3 months for any financial gain or salaries. <br/></li><li>Any employee found providing false and misleading information in relation to any claim for release on medical ground, In the case of violation of any declaration and promises above, employee will stand to pay INR 1,50,000 for the breach of trust and declaration to Ray Business Technologies Pvt Ltd. You may also be liable to all court lawsuit expenses in case of any legal procedures. <br/></li></ol><p></p><div><br/></div><p><b>Separation Process in OVH</b></p><p>Associates can submit his/ her resignation through Separation Module in OVH, no emails will be entertained.</p><p>Steps to be followed:</p><p></p><ol><li>Associate need to login to OVH, then click on Separation Module.</li><li>He / she can request for separation by filling up the resignation form in Submit/ View Resignation page.</li><li>Once the associate submit the resignation, email notification will be sent to reporting manager.</li><li>Reporting Manager will have an offline discussion with the concern and the same will be updated in the comments.</li><li>Then the delivery manager and HR will have an offline discussion with the resigned employee and update the comments.</li><li>On the relieving date, HR will initiate the relieving and Reporting Manager, IT, HR, Accounts and Admin department are requested to update the clearance certificate on or before 15 working days.</li><li>Employee is requested to fill up the Exit feedback form and submit the same to HR department.</li><li>Once the HR collect the details, the relieving confirmation will be e-mailed to the associate on the same day and the relieving letter will be posted to the address provided by him/her after getting no-due clearance from his/her Reporting Manager, Accounts, IT, Admin and HR departments.</li></ol><div>For further queries, please feel free to contact HR department.</div><div><br/></div><div><div>Relieving letters will be posted, Associates has to furnish their address in OVH. The first attempt will be free. </div><div><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">In case your address in not updated in OVH, any official postal communication failure is solely your responsibility. Raybiztech will not entertain any concern once it has experienced Postal return. While the first post is free for our associates, the company will deduct INR 500 against next each postal communication from your Full &amp; Final settlement.</span></div></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><b>Any changes in the amendments, HR department will be notifying all the  associates through email.</b></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><p></p>',
